<plot>The film poses the question: Should we only focus our attention on work and future ambitious plans, or is it also enjoying present life with its various spontaneous expressions that merits our attention? "My film is about being open in life... about grasping time and appreciating it...about not loosing human touch... about letting the heart open despite work pressures... Only then one can be ready for destiny surprises... only then one can fully live... and sometimes it is only a matter of time for things to click or things to happen!" L. E. Cordero</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?167710</url></doc>
